  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UserPreferencesInstance
extends UserPreferences
    Instantiation of the UserPreferences template object. These objects are similar, but we keep the distinction between template and instances explicitly. Operations by controllers are performed on instances, not templates.
